On 27 September 2014 a 4 year old girl, O.S.P., was nearly beaten to death by her step-father,Mr. D.V.N, 26 years old, worker at Thnorl Bek village, Kar Krov Sankat, Doun Koe town, Takao province,Mr. D.V.N claimed he had simply reprimanded his 4 year step-daughter for playing too close to the road.
However, Mr. D.V.N.’s neighbors stated that he had beaten 4 year old O.S.P. for 2 consecutive days on the 25 and 26 September because her face resembled that of her biological father.
The perpetrator was arrested after the 4 year old victim’s family filled a complaint at the court.
ADHOC is investigating the case and is providing legal assistance to the victim and will keep following up this case. 